These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, july, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, cola, iced-tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, siglo, baccarat
 1. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Birthday   | april | march    | december   | july    |
| Beverage           | cola       | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate   | lemonade     |
| Cigar     | alhambra       | swisher | baccarat  | siglo      |

