.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, american, chinese
House: tower, ranch-style, gothic-revival, colonial
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, dahlia, azalea
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the spanish##1
 4. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
 5. the american is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the tower house is between the colonial house and the dutch##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the colonial house##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Nationality      | dutch       | spanish | chinese     | american     |
| House   | ranch-style      | tower       | colonial | gothic-revival |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Flower     | azalea | dahlia     | daisy     | zinnia       |

