.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, bellflower, dahlia
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, singing, baking, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, journalist, engineer
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 3. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
 4. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is between the engineer and the journalist##2
 7. the fisherman is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Flower          | dahlia    | bellflower      | lily   | marigold |
| Hobby   | gardening | baking | singing | sudoku  |
| Job   | nurse   | journalist         | fisherman  | engineer  |
| Pet           | pony      | dog          | turtle | lizard  |

