.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: radish, corn, banana, onion
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, skateboard, scooter
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, indian, turkish
 1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 3. the mexican is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the turkish##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Food           | corn    | onion   | banana | radish |
| Transport   | scooter      | jet-ski    | bus        | skateboard         |
| Nationality         | japanese    | indian | turkish         | mexican    |

