 3. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 5. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 6. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 7. the photographer is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 8. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 9. the person eating peas is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
11. the cottage house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
12. the nurse is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
