 3. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 4. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the fan of jazz is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 9. the chef is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
10. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
12. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
13. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5

