There are 4 different nationalities: american, german, polish, thai
City: edinburgh, boston, hamburg, miami
 1. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person driving the bus##2
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 6. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 7. the german is on the far left##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
 9. the polish is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
12. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
13. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |    4     |
