.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, salsa, dubstep
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lavender, orange, blue
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, horse, hedgehog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the owner of the goat is between the fan of country and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 4. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
 6. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the owner of the goat is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
12. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Music-Genre      | dubstep   | country | metal   | salsa          |
| Color          | lavender    | blue        | orange     | aquamarine          |
| Pet           | goldfish | horse        | goat | hedgehog |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

