.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, turquise, brown, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, baseball, snowboarding, volleyball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, swisher, dunhill
 1. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes brown and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes brown is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Color           | black   | emerald  | turquise        | brown |
| Sport   | climbing     | volleyball     | snowboarding      | baseball   |
| Cigar     | blend | swisher | dunhill          | montecristo     |

