.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, pall-mall, game
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, go, backgammon
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, aquamarine, chestnut
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 2. the person who likes chestnut is the cain-smoker##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 7. the social-worker is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
10. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
11. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
12. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar          | cain | pall-mall  | game    | vegafina       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Game   | canasta    | go   | backgammon  | mah-jongg     |
| Color   | chestnut      | aquamarine    | blood-red        | red |

 